    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't looking for a show car. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading in the clear coat on the hood, while the interior shows clear signs of use, including some wear on the driver's seat and carpet. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, though it could benefit from a tune-up and some minor suspension work in the near future. It is a solid, functional car that reflects its age and mileage honestly.",
