    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid choice for anyone seeking practical transportation. It's a functional, budget-friendly option that still has plenty of life left to give!",
